<br />

<br />
Question, should I augment just about everything I own with INT or Mana Items, or plop down the cash for Flowing Thought items? I don't see too many peices under a 100k on my server though...
<br />

<br />
Or just hit 65 and save AA's for Mental Clarity etc....</span></td>
