				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Ding 63! Ding AA 12! Ding FM!<a name="32553"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 2 04 1:46 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>FT &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Int.  Cant say that enough.  Fade is 900 mana.  Buckarsed nekkid you should have enough mana for 2 fades.  With gear probably 3.  If you need to Fade 3 times in a row, you are probably doing something wrong.  Sure it is nice to have the ability to fade 5 times in a row, but WHY?  Regenning what mana you have fast is more important.
<br />

<br />
But dont go all out apeshit trying to get FT items imho.  If you are a decent puller, you shouldnt HAVE to fade a lot.  If you toss in song of dawn once in a while, you shouldnt need Fade to get off Ramp aggro either.
<br />
You can get the slot 7 FT aug in LDoN from Mir.
<br />
If you dont have MC1, make that your next AA, if you dont have any Ft, MC1 will double your mana regen.
<br />
I certainly wouldnt pay even 50k for an FT item.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
